msgstr "Komponenta puta"

msgid ""
"The numbering starts from 1, e.g. on the page admin/structure/types, "
"the 3rd path component is \"types\"."
msgstr ""
"Numeriranje počinje od 1, npr. na stranici admin/structure/types, "
"treći dio puta je \"types\"."

