msgstr ""
"Prihvaća bilo koji datum u bilo kojem <a "
"href=\"https://www.gnu.org/software/tar/manual/html_chapter/tar_7.html#Date-input-formats\">GNU "
"formatu unosa datuma</a>. Nizovi poput today, +2 months i Dec 9 2004 "
"svi su valjani."

msgid ""
"The @title could not be interpreted in <a "
"href=\"https://www.gnu.org/software/tar/manual/html_chapter/tar_7.html#Date-input-formats\">GNU "
"Date Input Format</a>."
msgstr ""
"@title se nije mogao protumačiti u <a "
"href=\"https://www.gnu.org/software/tar/manual/html_chapter/tar_7.html#Date-input-formats\">GNU "
"formatu unosa datuma</a>."

