"Enter time format using <a "
"href=\"http://php.net/manual/en/function.date.php\">Time Input "
"Format</a>."
msgstr ""
"Unesite format vremena koristeći <a "
"href=\"http://php.net/manual/en/function.date.php\">Format unosa "
"vremena</a>."

